videos.description: NC State's Dennis Smith Jr. makes a contested shot, gets a steal and score and knocks down a 3-pointer for the Wolfpack.
videos.headline: Smith Jr. does it all for NC State

videos.description: North Carolina's Luke Maye draws the defender with the pump fake and finishes with the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Maye sweet pump fake results in strong dunk

videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II hits a 3-pointer to help increase the lead for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Berry II hits 3 to pad the lead
